gtkmm widgets, music oriented.

CloWidget::CloExpander : Support fullscreen, mouse resize, mouse move
CloWidget::CloKnob
CloWidget::CloSlider
CloWidget::CloButton : A fuckin button (support toggle too)
CloWidget::CloArea : A widget area (that dynamically arrange all child widgets)
CloWidget::CloPlugin : Embbed a plugin GUI
CloWidget::CloGroup : A group of simple widget (knob/slider/button) (supporting slime/wide interface)
